# Home Virtual Lab Setup

## Project Overview
This project demonstrates how to build a home virtual lab.
It is designed for beginners to practice IT fundamentals like networking, operating systems, and system administration.

## Tools Used
- Vmware Workstation
- Kali Linux (VM)

## FOLLOW THE SEQUENCE
Step 1: Download VMware Workstation
        -Create a Broadcom account.
        -Log in and navigate to the My Downloads section.
        -Locate and download VMware Workstation Pro from the available downloads.
         Note: VMware is only licensed for individual purposes.

Step 2: Download Kali Linux ISO
        - Open Kali Linux Official Website
        - Choose Installer Images as Platform
        - Download Installer ISO

